# Load package
import cv2
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np


# -------------Type your code here-------------
# TODO: load image "winnie.jpeg", place it in variable "image"
image = cv2.imread("winnie.jpeg")

# --------------------------------

(b, g, r) = image[0, 0]
print("Pixel at (0, 0) - Red: {}, Green: {}, Blue: {}".format(r,g, b))
image[0, 0] = (0, 0, 255)
(b, g, r) = image[0, 0]
print("Pixel at (0, 0) - Red: {}, Green: {}, Blue: {}".format(r,g, b))

#--------code for showing image------------

# transfer BGR to RGB 
# (Because plt show image in RGB, but opencv load image in BGR)
image = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)

# set image to show
plt.imshow(image)
# set title
plt.title("Winnie the Pooh")
# show image
plt.show()

# 为了以后方便显示，把显示方法放入show_image方法中
# title 图片标题，image 存储图片的数组
def show_image(title,image):
    image = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)
    # set image to show
    plt.imshow(image)
    # set title
    plt.title(title)
    # show image
    plt.show()

# show Origin image    
image = cv2.imread("./winnie.jpeg")
show_image("Origin",image)

canvas = np.zeros((300,300,3), dtype = "uint8")
canvas = cv2.bitwise_not(canvas)
#不知道爲什麼我用np.ones沒起作用，還是給我建個黑板，求解

题目二¶

  • 考察内容：
    • Translation
    • Rotation
    • Resizing
    • Flipping
    • Cropping
In [4]:
image = cv2.imread("./winnie.jpeg")
show_image("Origin",image)

# -------------Type your code below-------------------
# 1.向右50 pixel，向上90 pixel
M = np.float32([[1,0,50],[0,1,-90]])
shifted = cv2.warpAffine(image,M,(image.shape[1],image.shape[0]))
show_image("Shifted Up and Right",shifted)

# 2.上一次修改后的图形绕中心顺时针旋转45度
(h,w) = shifted.shape[:2]
center = (w // 2 , h // 2)

M = cv2.getRotationMatrix2D(center , -45 ,1.0 )
rotated = cv2.warpAffine(shifted , M , (w,h))
show_image("Rotated by 45 Degrees",rotated)

# 3.上一次修改后的图形按照宽度（width）变成200 pixel进行等比例缩小(使用)
r = 200.0 / rotated.shape[1]
dim = (150 , int(rotated.shape[0] * r))
resized = cv2.resize(rotated ,dim ,interpolation = cv2.INTER_AREA)
show_image("Resize Width",resized)

# 4.上一次修改后的图形水平对称图片(使用)
flipped = cv2.flip(resized , 1)
show_image("Flipped Horizontally",flipped)

# 5.在上一次修改后的图形中把小熊维尼的头像剪切出来
cropped =flipped[10:70 , 52:95]
show_image("Winnie's Face",cropped)

题目三¶

  • 考察内容：
    • Image arithmetic
    • Bitwise Operation
In [5]:
show_image("Origin",image)

# -------------Type your code below-------------------

# 原图片所有的像素点数值加20
M = np.ones(image.shape , dtype = "uint8") *20
addImage = cv2.add(image , M)
show_image("Add 20 intensity",addImage)

# 原图片所有的像素点数值减20
subImage = cv2.subtract(image,M)
show_image("Subtract 20 intensity",subImage)

# addImage 和 subImage 进行亦或处理
bitwiseXor = cv2.bitwise_xor(addImage , subImage)
show_image("bitwise xor",bitwiseXor)

# -------------Type your code below-------------------
# 1.create mask's canvas
mask = np.zeros(image.shape[:2] , dtype = "uint8")
(cX,cY) = (image.shape[1] // 2  ,image.shape[0] // 2 )
cv2.circle(mask , (cX , cY) , 200 ,255 ,-1)

#----------show mask(Don't Change any of these)--------
plt.title("mask")
plt.imshow(mask,cmap = plt.cm.gray)
plt.show()
#-----------------------------------------------------

# 2.Place mask
masked = cv2.bitwise_and(image , image , mask = mask)
show_image("Mask Applied to Image",masked)

  • 考察内容：

In [7]:
# -------------Type your code below-------------------
# Split the image
# 将图片拆分成B、G、R，用彩色图分别显示
show_image("Origin",image)
(B,G,R) = cv2.split(image)
zeros = np.zeros(image.shape[:2] , dtype = "uint8")
show_image("Red",cv2.merge([zeros , zeros , R]))
show_image("Green",cv2.merge([zeros , G , zeros]))
show_image("Blue",cv2.merge([B , zeros , zeros]))
